@startuml C4_Ops_IncidentResponse
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml

title YAWL Operations - Incident Response Lifecycle

Boundary(detection, "Detection Phase") {
    Component(monitoring, "Monitoring Alert", "Detection", "Metric crosses threshold")
    Component(alert_notification, "Alert Notification", "Escalation", "Slack/PagerDuty")
    Component(incident_creation, "Incident Creation", "Jira", "Create ticket")
}

Boundary(triage, "Triage Phase") {
    Component(on_call, "On-Call Engineer", "Responder", "Assigned to incident")
    Component(initial_assessment, "InitialAssessment", "Analysis", "Severity 1-5")
    Component(runbook_lookup, "RunbookLookup", "Procedures", "Find applicable runbook")
}

Boundary(investigation, "Investigation Phase") {
    Component(metric_analysis, "MetricAnalysis", "Data", "Analyze metrics")
    Component(log_analysis, "LogAnalysis", "Data", "Search logs")
    Component(trace_analysis, "TraceAnalysis", "Data", "Trace request flow")
    Component(root_cause, "RootCauseAnalysis", "Reasoning", "Identify root cause")
}

Boundary(mitigation, "Mitigation Phase") {
    Component(immediate_fix, "ImmediateFix", "Action", "Stop the bleeding")
    Component(remediation, "Remediation", "Action", "Fix the problem")
    Component(verification, "Verification", "Testing", "Verify fix works")
    Component(status_update, "StatusUpdate", "Communication", "Notify stakeholders")
}

Boundary(postmortem, "Post-Mortem Phase") {
    Component(postmortem_meeting, "PostMortemMeeting", "Retrospective", "Team discussion")
    Component(root_cause_doc, "RootCauseDoc", "Documentation", "Record findings")
    Component(lessons_learned, "LessonsLearned", "Learning", "Prevention measures")
    Component(action_items, "ActionItems", "Improvement", "Prevent recurrence")
}

monitoring --> alert_notification: Triggers
alert_notification --> incident_creation: Creates
incident_creation --> on_call: Assigns to
on_call --> initial_assessment: Triages
initial_assessment --> runbook_lookup: Follows
runbook_lookup --> metric_analysis: Starts investigation
metric_analysis --> root_cause: Feeds into
root_cause --> immediate_fix: Informs
immediate_fix --> remediation: Leads to
remediation --> verification: Validates
verification --> status_update: Communicates
status_update --> postmortem_meeting: Schedules
postmortem_meeting --> root_cause_doc: Documents
root_cause_doc --> lessons_learned: Extracts
lessons_learned --> action_items: Creates

Note as N1
Incident Response Lifecycle:

Detection (1-2 min):
- Monitoring alert triggered
- PagerDuty notification
- Incident ticket created

Triage (5 min):
- On-call engineer assigned
- Severity assessment (1=critical, 5=minor)
- Runbook retrieved

Investigation (10-30 min):
- Analyze metrics
- Search logs
- Trace request flow
- Identify root cause

Mitigation (10-60 min):
- Stop the bleeding (immediate fix)
- Fix the problem (remediation)
- Verify fix works
- Notify stakeholders

Post-Mortem (Next day):
- Team discussion (why did it happen)
- Document findings
- Extract lessons learned
- Create action items to prevent recurrence

SLOs:
- Detection: <2 minutes
- Triage: <5 minutes
- Investigation: <30 minutes
- Mitigation: <60 minutes
- MTTR (Mean Time To Recovery): <1 hour

Root Causes:
- 70%: Code bugs (fix in PR)
- 20%: Config errors (update runbook)
- 10%: External failures (document expected behavior)
End note

SHOW_LEGEND()
@enduml
